org.jhove2.app.util.traverser
Class ReportableTypeTraverser

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.app.util.traverser.ReportableTypeTraverser

public class ReportableTypeTraverser
extends Object

Traverses static code of a Reportable class to extract feature information. NOTE: can only detect inner reportable classes to one level of nesting

Author:
smorrissey
